value.0: This axe bears the mark of Metamorpha Stonehammer, smith of the Benzor Mountains.  She designed it specifically to deal maximum damage to orcs.

This axe bears the stamp of Metamorpha Stonehammer.  

Metamorpha calls this weapon her pride n' joy.  She has carefully honed the edge to such sharpness that it will cut through steel like a hot knife through butter.  Just holding the weapon in your hand gives you a feeling of imperviousness.

This axe has the stamp of Metamorpha Stonehammer, master smith of the Benzor Mountains.

She got tired of scaring off Frost Giants from her part of the mountains, so she crafted this axe to kill them dead.
This is a cooked steak.  You cannot tell which animal it came from.
